com.yworks.yfiles.graph

Class GraphItemTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Number
      • com.yworks.yfiles.utils.FlagsEnum<GraphItemTypes>
        • com.yworks.yfiles.graph.GraphItemTypes
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class GraphItemTypes
extends FlagsEnum<GraphItemTypes>
    An enumeration for use in various properties that can take a bitwise combination of item types that make up an IGraph.

    The enumeration can be used to create bitwise combination of the types.

    See Also:
